  <brief_title>Clinical Study to Evaluate the Efficacy of HUDC_VT in Patients With Bacterial Vaginosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Parallel Design, Multicenter Phase II Trial to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of HUDC_VT in Patients With Bacterial Vaginosis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
